12 different output ports can meet all your needs simultaneously. 30A AC Outlet design for RV travel, 4 AC ports with a wattage of up to 3600W (Peak 6000W) for almost all home appliances, 2 USB-C charging ports, 4 USB-A ports, and 1 car outlets for small devices. No more anxiety about electricity.

With proprietary AP-POWER technology, ALLPOWERS R4000 can be charged from 0 to 100% in just 1 hour by EV station charging & solar or wall outlets & solar together, faster than any other solar generator. It can be charged wherever with 5 alternative charging ways and 3 charging mode.

  • 🔋【Unique Voice Control, Smart APP Control】

The world's first voice control system makes the operation more intelligent. Easily realized by connecting to ALLPOWERS APP through WIFI Power Monitoring/Function Setting/Remote Control/System Upgrade.

  • 🔋【UPS Function and Eco Mode】

ALLPOWERS R4000 equipped with Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) function. When wall outlet is interrupted, UPS will supply 110V AC power to the load in less than 15ms, protecting devices from damage. Eco mode can stop the internal power consumption, so R4000 can retain power for a longer time without frequent charging.
